{"tid":1782492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網絡戰唔好淨係停留喺「鬥多like」級數","createTime":"2019-12-14T04:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T19:02:52.000Z","uid":71237,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e04ca67a53a8a3f47afc1800e792bd1e7febcd3e","tid":1782492,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:01:05.000Z","msg":"今日足球球星奧斯爾ig貼咗支持東突的post，引來大批大陸人ig批鬥。<br />\n部份連登仔諗到嘅只係用大陸人喺ig鬥鬧、刷comments。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1782314/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1782314/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n首先大陸有14億人，你用「鬥人多」的方式去戰鬥本身已經處於劣勢。<br />\n更何況ig幾萬個comments根本無人會睇，你以為自己花全日喺ig留言就係聲援緊奧斯爾，但奧斯爾根本唔會逐個comments睇。你需要做嘅係將依件事擴散，將大陸人的極端言論翻譯做英文喺Twitter、ig廣傳。<br />\n<br />\n好多連登仔對網絡戰仍然停留喺「鬥多like」「鬥投票」的階段。<br />\n例如藍絲Facebook page同傳媒成日搞投票，依種垃圾投票的結果從來都無人關注。<br />\n但有啲連登仔次次都好認真咁號召幾千人去投，又誇大重要性。<br />\n例如下面依兩個post：<br />\n連登仔連網戰都輸，醜唔醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1685156/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1685156/page/1</a><br />\n[大件事！！！] 有樣野輸緊！！！入黎幫幫手！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1779958/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1779958/page/1</a><br />\n與其鬥投票，不如將啲時間擺喺其他有用的地方。<br />\n<br />\n好多連登仔亦都好驚五毛成功喺Facebook、YouTube、ig用comments帶風向。<br />\n我見過唔少post呼籲手足喺Facebook、YouTube、ig like自己人的comments。<br />\n但係我想講，留言根本無咩人睇，亦都唔會輕易令人改變立場。<br />\n你與其不斷留言，不如出多幾個post。出一個post比留言有用1000倍。<br />\n你有時間同大陸人喺YouTube鬥多comments，不如將啲時間用嚟製作多一條影片。<br />\n你有時間同大陸人喺ig鬥多comments，不如ig share幾張靚嘅英文文宣，善用hashtag比多啲人睇到。"},{"pid":"879b93ea08c54ea242207655c5fa322a26e9c897","tid":1782492,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:01:13.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5de78652535fd9b12593cf7d05f98d52e85e85e1","tid":1782492,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:01:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該推行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyqyGMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyqyGMZ.jpg&h=2f6dc79b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"649a1a8a605a3a1ea1e22df136ac6a1b3c839cb2","tid":1782492,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"如果想學下點樣玩網絡戰，不如睇下依個post。<br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士唔應該停留喺低成本抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1775722/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1775722/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c9098ae4b6472213c54f4e52b4917b540af8ff84","tid":1782492,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc754dcdb5c2f40ce81b13bcca1ece07de237c67","tid":1782492,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫推"},{"pid":"d8cddca840e8108409875b852a0215b1be7e098c","tid":1782492,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:03:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3dc72e0da704d678e7d6a78e53bcc2122e9c518","tid":1782492,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:04:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d7601ac3184cc3c3235c1d36fcaaae7758e5230","tid":1782492,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649a1a8a605a3a1ea1e22df136ac6a1b3c839cb2","tid":1782492,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"如果想學下點樣玩網絡戰，不如睇下依個post。<br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士唔應該停留喺低成本抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1775722/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1775722/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"Pin"},{"pid":"87fa6f7fca6ee7f891605ae4e2c4557b01655248","tid":1782492,"uid":71237,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"最近有個comment真係令我好深刻印象。<br />\n我叫巴打唔好理藍絲page啲垃圾投票，跟住有巴打覆我「如果連簡單投票都輸，做咩鍵盤戰士」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owPzrhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FowPzrhW.png&h=5fff2178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依種諗法根本係常見謬誤。你捉過棋都知道唔係只進不退。<br />\n打仗都唔一定要每一場大小戰役都贏哂。<br />\n我們需要嘅係贏重要、有關鍵性的戰役。好minor、完全無重要性的地方可以放棄，將兵力放喺真正重要的地方。<br />\n<br />\n好似田忌賽馬咁，你依種諗法就好似田忌堅持三場都要贏哂，唔接受孫臏輸一場贏兩場的提議。<br />\n你咁鍾意投票，不如你自己又舉辦一堆投票，你咪做到大勝的效果囉。"},{"pid":"0de7b8383b2e2c7e5d647e5a50756042b19678a0","tid":1782492,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:09:00.000Z","msg":"一直我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好人好者 有咩人會無啦啦睇經濟日報 有咩人會係yahoo同支那人討論政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e50ca8edf6390d7c77404db3a83997faa573ba4","tid":1782492,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"d53e242bbde48a3ae28982ea87e45abfab857dd2","tid":1782492,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"有啲手足可能覺得自己無乜技能。<br />\n唔識拍片，唔識整文宣，唔識英文，唔識寫文章，又無電腦技能，淨係識like同share。<br />\n<br />\n首先唔識你可以學，香港人喺人數上已經處於劣勢，你要升級解鎖更高級嘅兵種先贏到。其他巴打有唔同嘅戰線都有提供教學，得閒應該揀樣嘢嚟學下。<br />\n<br />\n又或者你嘅戰場唔一定係網絡世界，你有體能又承擔到風險可以考慮勇武，無體能可以整連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n如果咩都做唔到，你不如去返工然後捐錢比義士或者幫襯黃店。咁樣仲有用過你喺ig同大陸人互鬧。"},{"pid":"78503b366bdd15dca2d9cc43608ac28695e396b3","tid":1782492,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:29:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fba7b32b242544c62443aab985160c7